    dc:description "FIGURE 3.Phylogenetic placement of Damas cervelina inthe treesconstructed from protein-coding regionsina)Z chromosome and b) mitochondrial genome: Carystina (blue) with D. cervelina (magenta, highlighted in yellow), and Hesperiina (green) with Megaleas syrna (purple). The clade of Damas is labeled. See Fig. 1 legend for other notations." ;
